column5: I just cleaned this paintin up a bit for a contest I'm entering  Look OK? You can be honest--won't hurt my feelings.

Again dude you capture what it is to be outdoors , what can be better than trout jumping into morning sun ,keep it up guy you paint from my heart, loved the last pic poor dude with flowers , hundred dollar bills will go much farther these days AHHHHHHHH ,but you know flowers will get the gooduns . B

Thats awesome work bushart. I think that is my favourite piece I have seen yet by you. Good luck in the contest. Awesome job on the splash that must have been hard to get that so detailed.  I am really impressed with that piece.

Very nice.  You said honest,so.  Did the fish miss the fly,or did the hook set go wrong,or did the fish spit the fly.  IMO It looks like the fish spit the fly/fly came out of the fishes yap.Fish looks real angry non the less.   It,s still a real nice painting Terrance.   Best of luck.
